# 🍔 eFoods — Full System Blueprint (From Scratch)

This document provides a complete technical map for building the **eFoods** platform, a cloud-native food ordering and delivery system using a **Microservices Architecture**.

---

## 🏗️ System Architecture Overview

The system consists of **6 independent backends** communicating via REST APIs (with potential for message queues like RabbitMQ as it scales) and **2 React-based frontends**.

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Customer Web App\nReact + Vite] --> B[Restaurant Service]
    A --> C[Order Service]
    A --> D[Payment Service]
    E[Driver Web App\nReact + Vite] --> F[Delivery Service]
    A --> G[Reviews Service]
    A --> H[Loyalty Service]

    subgraph "Main Persistence Cluster (MongoDB Atlas)"
        B_DB[(Restaurant DB)]
        C_DB[(Order DB)]
        F_DB[(Delivery DB)]
        D_DB[(Payment DB)]
        G_DB[(Reviews DB)]
        H_DB[(Loyalty DB)]
    end

    B --- B_DB
    C --- C_DB
    F --- F_DB
    D --- D_DB
    G --- G_DB
    H --- H_DB
```

---

## 🚦 System Port Map

To run all parts simultaneously on one machine, each service is assigned a unique port:

| Component | Port | Description |
|---|---|---|
| **Restaurant Management** | `5000` | Menu, images, restaurant info |
| **Order Management** | `5001` | Cart, Users, Order placement |
| **Delivery Management** | `5002` | Driver login, location, order claiming |
| **Payment & Notifications**| `5003` | Stripe integration, SMS, Email |
| **Reviews & Ratings** | `5004` | Customer feedback, star ratings |
| **Loyalty & Promotions** | `5005` | Discount coupons, points system |
| **Customer Web App** | `5173` | Main ordering portal |
| **Driver Web App** | `5174` | Driver dashboard & map tracking |

---

## 📦 Microservce Details (The "6 Core Units")

### 1. 🍽️ Restaurant Management Service (Port 5000)
*   **Purpose:** Manages the menu and restaurant profiles.
*   **Key Tech:** Express, MongoDB, **Multer** (for food image uploads).
*   **Models:** [Restaurant.js](file:///d:/GitHub/efoods-online-food-ordering-and-delivery-management-system/restaurant-management-service-neranda/backend/models/Restaurant.js), [MenuItem.js](file:///d:/GitHub/efoods-online-food-ordering-and-delivery-management-system/restaurant-management-service-neranda/backend/models/MenuItem.js).
*   **Key Endpoints:**
    *   `GET /api/restaurants` — List all restaurants.
    *   `POST /api/menu` — Add a new food item.
    *   `GET /api/menu?restaurantId=...` — Get menu for one spot.

### 2. 🛒 Order Management Service (Port 5001)
*   **Purpose:** The core engine for users and their transactions.
*   **Key Tech:** Express, MongoDB, **JWT** (Authentication).
*   **Models:** [User.js](file:///d:/GitHub/efoods-online-food-ordering-and-delivery-management-system/order-management-service-sasin/backend/models/User.js), [Cart.js](file:///d:/GitHub/efoods-online-food-ordering-and-delivery-management-system/order-management-service-sasin/backend/models/Cart.js), [Order.js](file:///d:/GitHub/efoods-online-food-ordering-and-delivery-management-system/order-management-service-sasin/backend/models/Order.js).
*   **Key Endpoints:**
    *   `POST /api/auth/register` — Create customer account.
    *   `POST /api/cart` — Add item to basket.
    *   `POST /api/orders` — Place the actual order.

### 3. 🚚 Delivery Management Service (Port 5002)
*   **Purpose:** For riders to manage their jobs and update location.
*   **Key Tech:** Express, MongoDB, **Google Maps API**.
*   **Models:** `Driver.js`, `ActiveDelivery.js`.
*   **Key Endpoints:**
    *   `GET /api/drivers/available-orders` — See what needs delivering.
    *   `POST /api/drivers/claim-order` — Grab a delivery job.
    *   `PUT /api/drivers/location` — Send current GPS coordinates.

### 4. 💳 Payment & Notification Service (Port 5003)
*   **Purpose:** Secure money handling and updates.
*   **Key Tech:** **Stripe API**, **Twilio** (SMS), **Nodemailer** (Email).
*   **Models:** [Payment.js](file:///d:/GitHub/efoods-online-food-ordering-and-delivery-management-system/payment-and-notification-management-service-ishara/backend/models/Payment.js) (Transaction history).
*   **Key Endpoints:**
    *   `POST /api/payment/checkout` — Create Stripe session.
    *   `POST /api/payment/webhook` — Automate order "Paid" status.

### 5. ⭐ Reviews & Ratings Service (Port 5004)
*   **Purpose:** Manages transparency and trust.
*   **Key Tech:** Express, MongoDB.
*   **Models:** `Review.js`.
*   **Key Endpoints:**
    *   `POST /api/reviews` — Rate a restaurant (1-5 stars).
    *   `GET /api/reviews/:restaurantId` — Show user comments.

### 6. 🎁 Loyalty & Promotions Service (Port 5005)
*   **Purpose:** Marketing and user retention.
*   **Key Tech:** Express, MongoDB.
*   **Models:** `Coupon.js`, `UserPoints.js`.
*   **Key Endpoints:**
    *   `POST /api/promo/validate` — Apply code like `FIRST50`.
    *   `POST /api/loyalty/points` — Earn points on purchase.

